WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

2
00:00:30.651 --> 00:00:35.780
Hail Mary. full of grace. the Lord is with thee.

3
00:00:36.405 --> 00:00:39.575
Blessed art thou among women.

4
00:00:39.700 --> 00:00:42.160
and blessed is the fruit of thy womb Jesus.

5
00:00:43.703 --> 00:00:48.415
Holy Mary. Mother of God. pray for us sinners.

6
00:00:53.127 --> 00:00:55.504
Now and at the hour of our death.

7
00:04:10.368 --> 00:04:11.536
Help!

8
00:04:45.563 --> 00:04:47.606
Please...

9
00:04:49.400 --> 00:04:51.693
...help.

10
00:06:14.885 --> 00:06:16.260
What a waste.

11
00:06:17.178 --> 00:06:18.805
Look at her.

12
00:06:18.805 --> 00:06:48.805
<b>Subtitle | www.movieddl.me</b>

13
00:06:56.876 --> 00:06:58.336
Sister Cecilia.

14
00:06:58.461 --> 00:06:59.671
Apologies.

15
00:06:59.796 --> 00:07:01.296
I'm Deacon Enzo. Come with me.

16
00:07:37.284 --> 00:07:38.201
How much longer?

17
00:07:38.618 --> 00:07:40.035
We're almost there.

18
00:08:27.407 --> 00:08:28.867
Right this way. Sister Cecilia.

19
00:08:39.417 --> 00:08:40.751
Sister Cecilia!

20
00:08:44.379 --> 00:08:47.798
Your eyes radiate the light of the Holy Spirit.

21
00:08:48.299 --> 00:08:51.384
Like the angels delivered you
straight from the heavens.

22
00:08:51.760 --> 00:08:54.304
We've been eagerly awaiting your arrival.
my dear.

23
00:09:06.730 --> 00:09:09.399
Isabelle. will you please show Cecilia
to her room?

24
00:09:09.733 --> 00:09:12.526
I have to help our sisters get ready
for tonight's celebration.

25
00:09:12.652 --> 00:09:14.903
Mind your place and do as I ask!

26
00:09:47.596 --> 00:09:48.722
Hello. Sisters.

27
00:09:48.847 --> 00:09:50.848
This is our new novice. Sister Cecilia.

28
00:10:04.402 --> 00:10:06.027
Have you seen my daddy?

29
00:10:06.569 --> 00:10:10.239
Yes. let's go find him. shall we?

30
00:14:59.054 --> 00:15:04.391
In the name of the Father. the Son.
and the Holy Spirit.

31
00:20:44.954 --> 00:20:47.540
Sometimes we get caught up in emotion.

32
00:21:10.475 --> 00:21:13.353
Saint Helena. Mother of Constantine...

33
00:21:13.853 --> 00:21:15.604
...brought this back from Jerusalem.

34
00:21:16.647 --> 00:21:17.481
Here.

35
00:21:22.693 --> 00:21:24.737
He suffered on the cross.

36
00:21:41.583 --> 00:21:46.629
For you. For us. For our sins.
For our salvation.

37
00:21:49.715 --> 00:21:51.550
In the name of His love.

38
00:21:52.884 --> 00:21:54.010
It is a gift.

39
00:22:02.267 --> 00:22:03.726
Are you alright. Sister?

40
00:25:08.582 --> 00:25:12.460
Good morning. Sisters.
Today a new life begins.

41
00:25:13.336 --> 00:25:14.962
But this new year will not be easy.

42
00:25:15.713 --> 00:25:17.506
You will question your purpose.

43
00:25:17.631 --> 00:25:21.134
You will question me
and why you have come here.

44
00:25:21.759 --> 00:25:25.429
And some of you will not have
the spiritual fortitude for this life.

45
00:25:37.939 --> 00:25:40.024
Do you find this amusing. Sister Guendalina?

46
00:25:41.191 --> 00:25:42.443
No. forgive me.

47
00:25:42.568 --> 00:25:44.570
This side of the room is with me.

48
00:25:45.278 --> 00:25:49.240
The other. will serve with Sister Isabelle.

49
00:25:57.872 --> 00:25:59.831
Looks like her vibrator ran out of battery.

50
00:26:28.271 --> 00:26:31.398
First you have to make sure
your knife is nice and sharp.

51
00:26:31.523 --> 00:26:33.358
Otherwise you run the risk of making a big mess.

52
00:28:08.434 --> 00:28:10.227
Blessed.

53
00:28:11.145 --> 00:28:13.063
Saint.

54
00:28:13.856 --> 00:28:16.816
All of us adore you.

55
00:28:38.750 --> 00:28:41.794
Blessed Saint Cecilia.

56
00:31:23.716 --> 00:31:26.009
Sister Cecilia. Come with me.

57
00:32:00.578 --> 00:32:01.495
Your Eminence.

58
00:32:01.912 --> 00:32:02.913
Sit.

59
00:32:52.870 --> 00:32:54.330
Have you kept your vow of poverty?

60
00:32:57.123 --> 00:32:58.958
Have you remained chaste?

61
00:33:49.374 --> 00:33:51.792
When she arrived. Dr. Gallo.
did you examine her?

62
00:33:51.917 --> 00:33:53.168
Her hymen was intact.

63
00:33:53.502 --> 00:33:56.337
It's never been touched.

64
00:34:09.681 --> 00:34:12.892
Mother Superior. have we had
visitors during these last few weeks?

65
00:35:17.444 --> 00:35:19.154
This child was...

66
00:35:19.945 --> 00:35:22.239
...conceived without sin.

67
00:35:24.782 --> 00:35:26.201
As God as my witness...

68
00:35:28.328 --> 00:35:30.537
...we have been blessed with a miracle.

69
00:39:23.808 --> 00:39:27.227
It was supposed to be me! Bitch!

70
00:39:39.528 --> 00:39:40.362
Sisters!

71
00:39:40.487 --> 00:39:41.446
Stop it!

72
00:39:41.571 --> 00:39:42.698
Leave her alone!

73
00:39:43.240 --> 00:39:44.157
Stop!

74
00:39:46.701 --> 00:39:48.160
We have to try again!

75
00:39:48.285 --> 00:39:50.745
They have to try again with me!

76
00:39:51.079 --> 00:39:53.790
They have to try again with me!

77
00:41:47.881 --> 00:41:49.882
Bless you. young mother.

78
00:42:39.839 --> 00:42:41.090
All of you. go.

79
00:42:42.258 --> 00:42:43.759
Go away. I said!

80
00:43:36.509 --> 00:43:37.677
Don't touch me.

81
00:43:41.930 --> 00:43:44.891
How the fuck can you just stand there
as if nothing happened?

82
00:43:45.391 --> 00:43:47.476
Cecilia’s pregnant and we don't know how.

83
00:43:47.602 --> 00:43:49.895
Isabelle killed herself.
What the fuck is going on?

84
00:43:51.021 --> 00:43:53.440
Let go of me!
I know when a man is lying to me.

85
00:43:53.565 --> 00:43:57.109
And all of you. every single one of you.
is so full of bullshit!

86
00:43:57.234 --> 00:43:58.986
Let go of me! Let go of me!

87
00:43:59.111 --> 00:44:00.153
Let go of me!

88
00:44:01.654 --> 00:44:03.573
Let go of me! I said let me go!

89
00:49:46.930 --> 00:49:49.724
Let me go! Let me go!

90
00:49:58.982 --> 00:50:01.734
No. I'm begging you. please.

91
00:50:44.018 --> 00:50:45.560
Blessed...

92
00:51:54.366 --> 00:51:55.241
What's happening?

93
00:51:55.366 --> 00:51:56.242
I don't know.

94
00:51:58.077 --> 00:51:59.828
Mother! What's going on?

95
00:51:59.953 --> 00:52:01.246
I don't know. father.

96
00:52:07.543 --> 00:52:08.377
God in Heaven.

97
00:52:10.712 --> 00:52:11.504
Call Doctor Gallo.

98
00:52:11.629 --> 00:52:13.506
- It's not possible. it's Saturday.
- Call him!

99
00:52:13.631 --> 00:52:16.717
I won't get a hold of him. it's Saturday.
We need to get her to the hospital.

100
00:52:16.842 --> 00:52:18.885
- No.
- You must go. Now.

101
00:52:19.011 --> 00:52:20.970
- No.
- That's it. I'm calling an ambulance.

102
00:52:21.095 --> 00:52:22.263
Stop!

103
00:52:56.832 --> 00:52:58.792
What do we do if she dies on the way there?

104
00:52:59.959 --> 00:53:01.461
We must maintain hope.

105
00:53:02.587 --> 00:53:03.421
It ain't looking good.

106
00:53:03.546 --> 00:53:04.713
Then we shall pray.

107
00:54:08.473 --> 00:54:09.307
Yes.

108
00:54:30.073 --> 00:54:30.907
I understand.

109
00:54:37.704 --> 00:54:38.539
Stop the car.

110
00:54:39.164 --> 00:54:39.956
What?

111
00:54:40.081 --> 00:54:41.040
Stop the car.

112
00:55:49.220 --> 00:55:50.387
Now you're ashamed?

113
00:55:50.512 --> 00:55:51.346
Now?

114
00:55:52.014 --> 00:55:56.184
Where was your shame when you
stuffed a dead animal inside yourself?

115
00:55:59.519 --> 00:56:00.520
Shame on you.

116
00:56:00.937 --> 00:56:03.356
Making us believe the miracle died inside you.

117
00:56:04.274 --> 00:56:05.774
What do you have to say for yourself?

118
01:02:28.080 --> 01:02:29.289
Sister Cecilia.

119
01:04:17.751 --> 01:04:19.419
Any day now.

120
01:04:31.345 --> 01:04:33.723
I'll be right back with her medication.

121
01:04:36.099 --> 01:04:36.933
Would you care to?

122
01:04:37.809 --> 01:04:38.768
Yes!

123
01:04:59.576 --> 01:05:02.203
Such a beautiful mother. And those eyes.
Like sunflowers.

124
01:05:03.580 --> 01:05:04.955
Blessed child...

125
01:05:06.290 --> 01:05:08.167
...it's all part of His plan.

126
01:05:16.506 --> 01:05:21.928
Blessed are the meek.
for they shall inherit the earth.

126
01:05:22.305 --> 01:06:22.924
